    "id": "depth_three_layers_explicit",
    "category": "depth",
    "name_zh": "三层纵深",
    "summary": "前景 / 中景（主体）/ 后景三段式分层，让画面从 2D 变 3D",
    "axes": ["depth", "composition"],
    "scene_modes": ["portrait", "scenery", "documentary", "light_shadow"],
    "person_count_range": [0, 4],
    "priority": 5,
    "when_to_use": ["几乎所有非特写"],
    "evidence": "Michael Freeman 提出的三层结构是构建空间的最简模型；常见做法是前景半透明（树枝/路灯/窗框）",
    "watch_out": "前景不能压住主体面部；前景占画面≤20%；多层之间必须有景深差",
    "counter_example": "极简主义抽象画面（一面纯墙 + 一个人）反而要单层",
    "tags": ["三层", "纵深", "构图"],
    "citations": [
      { "source": "Michael Freeman《The Photographer's Eye》", "chapter": "Layers and Depth" }
    ],
